  user_input {
    user_response: "Here is a detailed AI agent prompt you can use with Claude Code, Cursor, Bolt, Lovable, v0, Windsurf, or any coding agent to generate the portfolio website.\n\n---\n\n# Portfolio Website Generation Prompt\n\nBuild a modern, premium, dark-themed portfolio website for:\n\n## Personal Information\n\n**Name:** Mohamed Irsath Kareem\n\n**Title:** Full Stack Web / Mobile App Developer\n\n---\n\n# Tech Stack Requirements\n\nMandatory:\n\n* ReactJS\n* TypeScript\n* Vite\n* TailwindCSS\n* React Router\n* Framer Motion\n* TanStack Query\n* React Intersection Observer\n* p5.js (for advanced interactive backgrounds and 3D-like visual effects)\n* Lucide React Icons\n\nOptional but preferred:\n\n* Zustand\n* React Three Fiber (if suitable)\n* Shadcn/UI\n\n---\n\n# Architecture Requirements\n\nFollow clean architecture principles.\n\n## Folder Structure\n\n```text\nsrc/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 app/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 routes/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 pages/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 components/\n\342\224\202   \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 common/\n\342\224\202   \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 sections/\n\342\224\202   \342\224\224\342\224\200\342\224\200 animations/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 data/\n\342\224\202   \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 repositories/\n\342\224\202   \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 sources/\n\342\224\202   \342\224\224\342\224\200\342\224\200 models/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 hooks/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 services/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 assets/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 utils/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 constants/\n\342\224\224\342\224\200\342\224\200 types/\n```\n\n---\n\n# Important Requirement\n\nDO NOT hardcode any content directly inside UI components.\n\nAll portfolio content must come from a dedicated data layer.\n\nExample:\n\n```typescript\ndata/\n \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 portfolio.ts\n \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 projects.ts\n \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 blogs.ts\n \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 skills.ts\n```\n\nUI components must only consume data.\n\nExample:\n\n```typescript\nconst projects = portfolioRepository.getProjects();\n```\n\nNever write:\n\n```tsx\n<h1>Mohamed Irsath Kareem</h1>\n```\n\nInstead:\n\n```tsx\n<h1>{profile.name}</h1>\n```\n\n---\n\n# Theme\n\nUse only one theme.\n\nDark theme only.\n\nDesign inspiration:\n\n* Linear\n* Vercel\n* Raycast\n* Stripe\n* Framer\n\nColor palette:\n\n```css\nBackground: #050816\nSurface: #0f172a\nPrimary: #38bdf8\nSecondary: #8b5cf6\nText: #f8fafc\nMuted: #94a3b8\n```\n\n---\n\n# Responsive Requirements\n\nMust support:\n\n* Mobile\n* Tablet\n* Desktop\n* Ultra Wide Monitors\n\nBreakpoints:\n\n```text\nsm\nmd\nlg\nxl\n2xl\n```\n\nEvery section must be responsive.\n\n---\n\n# Routing Structure\n\nUse React Router.\n\nRoutes:\n\n```text\n/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 Home\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 About\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 Projects\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 Blogs\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 Skills\n\342\224\224\342\224\200\342\224\200 Contact\n```\n\nOptional:\n\n```text\n/project/:slug\n/blog/:slug\n```\n\n---\n\n# Navbar\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Glassmorphism\n* Sticky\n* Blur effect\n* Animated active route indicator\n* Smooth route transitions\n\nDesktop:\n\n```text\nLogo\nHome\nAbout\nProjects\nBlogs\nSkills\nContact\n```\n\nMobile:\n\n```text\nHamburger Menu\nAnimated Drawer\n```\n\n---\n\n# Hero Section\n\nFull viewport section.\n\nDisplay:\n\n```text\nMohamed Irsath Kareem\n\nFull Stack Web /\nMobile App Developer\n```\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Typing animation\n* Gradient text\n* Floating particles\n* p5.js animated background\n* Mouse interaction effects\n* Scroll indicator\n\nCTA buttons:\n\n```text\nView Projects\nRead Blogs\nContact Me\n```\n\nAnimations:\n\n* Fade\n* Scale\n* Parallax\n* Stagger\n\n---\n\n# About Section\n\nProfessional introduction.\n\nHighlight:\n\n* Full Stack Development\n* Mobile Development\n* Cloud Native Engineering\n* DevOps\n\nTimeline layout.\n\nAnimated cards.\n\nStatistics:\n\n```text\nYears Experience\nProjects Built\nArticles Written\nTechnologies Used\n```\n\nCounter animations.\n\n---\n\n# Skills Section\n\nCreate categorized skill groups.\n\n## Frontend\n\n* ReactJS\n* TypeScript\n* JavaScript\n* Vite\n* NextJS\n* TanStack Query\n\n## Backend\n\n* Spring Boot\n* Java\n* Kotlin\n* Spring Cloud\n* SQL\n* NoSQL\n* Testing\n\n## DevOps\n\n* Docker\n* Kubernetes\n* Helm\n* Terraform\n* ArgoCD\n* AWS\n* GCP\n* Jenkins\n* GitHub Actions\n\n## Mobile\n\n* Jetpack Compose\n* Compose Multiplatform\n* Kotlin Multiplatform\n* Koin\n* Room\n* Ktor\n* Coil\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Animated skill cards\n* Hover effects\n* Progress indicators\n* Scroll reveal\n\n---\n\n# Projects Section\n\n## Mini Projects\n\nDisplay:\n\n```text\nJetpack Compose Animations\nCustom Layout Experiments\nCompose Multiplatform UI Showcases\nAnimation Labs\n```\n\nUse horizontal animated cards.\n\n---\n\n## Major Projects\n\n### Codehorn\n\nShow:\n\n```text\nTitle\nDescription\nTechnologies\nScreenshots\nGithub\nDemo\n```\n\n---\n\n### NoteMyShow\n\nShow:\n\n```text\nTitle\nDescription\nTechnologies\nScreenshots\nGithub\nDemo\n```\n\n---\n\n### Mobile Applications\n\nDisplay as project collection.\n\nUse masonry layout.\n\nAnimations:\n\n* Hover lift\n* Glow effect\n* Tilt effect\n* Stagger reveal\n\n---\n\n# Blogs Section\n\nSources:\n\n## Medium Articles\n\nDisplay:\n\n```text\nFeatured Articles\nLatest Articles\nPopular Articles\n```\n\n---\n\n## Internal Articles\n\nSupport:\n\n```text\nMarkdown Rendering\nSyntax Highlighting\nTable of Contents\nReading Time\n```\n\nBlog Cards:\n\n```text\nThumbnail\nTitle\nTags\nDate\nRead Time\n```\n\nAnimations:\n\n```text\nSlide Up\nFade In\nScale\n```\n\n---\n\n# Contact Section\n\nModern card layout.\n\nFields:\n\n```text\nName\nEmail\nSubject\nMessage\n```\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Validation\n* Animated inputs\n* Success animation\n\nAdditional links:\n\n```text\nGithub\nLinkedIn\nMedium\nEmail\n```\n\n---\n\n# Footer\n\nInclude:\n\n```text\nName\nTagline\nNavigation Links\nSocial Links\nCopyright\n```\n\nAnimated divider.\n\n---\n\n# Animation Requirements\n\nUse Framer Motion extensively.\n\nRequirements:\n\n### Scroll Animations\n\n```text\nFade Up\nFade Left\nFade Right\nScale\nRotate\n```\n\n### Hover Animations\n\n```text\nLift\nGlow\nMagnetic Button\nTilt Card\n```\n\n### Page Transitions\n\n```text\nRoute Transition\nShared Layout Animation\n```\n\n### Advanced\n\nUse Intersection Observer.\n\nTrigger animations only when visible.\n\n---\n\n# p5.js Requirements\n\nCreate an interactive background system.\n\nPossible effects:\n\n```text\nParticle Network\nConstellation\nFloating Dots\nInteractive Mouse Trails\n3D Wireframe Sphere\nNeural Network Visualization\n```\n\nPerformance optimized.\n\nDisable heavy effects on mobile.\n\n---\n\n# Performance Requirements\n\nImplement:\n\n```text\nLazy Loading\nCode Splitting\nMemoization\nImage Optimization\nRoute-based Chunking\n```\n\nUse:\n\n```typescript\nReact.lazy()\nSuspense\n```\n\n---\n\n# Accessibility\n\nImplement:\n\n```text\nARIA Labels\nKeyboard Navigation\nFocus States\nSemantic HTML\n```\n\n---\n\n# SEO\n\nAdd:\n\n```text\nMeta Tags\nOpenGraph Tags\nTwitter Tags\nStructured Data\nSitemap\nRobots.txt\n```\n\n---\n\n# Deliverables\n\nGenerate:\n\n1. Complete React + TypeScript project\n2. Tailwind configuration\n3. React Router setup\n4. Reusable component architecture\n5. Data layer implementation\n6. Responsive layouts\n7. Framer Motion animations\n8. p5.js interactive background\n9. Blog system architecture\n10. Production-ready codebase\n\nThe final result should feel like a premium developer portfolio comparable to Linear, Vercel, Framer, and modern SaaS landing pages, with smooth animations, strong visual hierarchy, dark aesthetic, and excellent performance.\n"
    items {
      text: "Here is a detailed AI agent prompt you can use with Claude Code, Cursor, Bolt, Lovable, v0, Windsurf, or any coding agent to generate the portfolio website.\n\n---\n\n# Portfolio Website Generation Prompt\n\nBuild a modern, premium, dark-themed portfolio website for:\n\n## Personal Information\n\n**Name:** Mohamed Irsath Kareem\n\n**Title:** Full Stack Web / Mobile App Developer\n\n---\n\n# Tech Stack Requirements\n\nMandatory:\n\n* ReactJS\n* TypeScript\n* Vite\n* TailwindCSS\n* React Router\n* Framer Motion\n* TanStack Query\n* React Intersection Observer\n* p5.js (for advanced interactive backgrounds and 3D-like visual effects)\n* Lucide React Icons\n\nOptional but preferred:\n\n* Zustand\n* React Three Fiber (if suitable)\n* Shadcn/UI\n\n---\n\n# Architecture Requirements\n\nFollow clean architecture principles.\n\n## Folder Structure\n\n```text\nsrc/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 app/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 routes/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 pages/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 components/\n\342\224\202   \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 common/\n\342\224\202   \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 sections/\n\342\224\202   \342\224\224\342\224\200\342\224\200 animations/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 data/\n\342\224\202   \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 repositories/\n\342\224\202   \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 sources/\n\342\224\202   \342\224\224\342\224\200\342\224\200 models/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 hooks/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 services/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 assets/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 utils/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 constants/\n\342\224\224\342\224\200\342\224\200 types/\n```\n\n---\n\n# Important Requirement\n\nDO NOT hardcode any content directly inside UI components.\n\nAll portfolio content must come from a dedicated data layer.\n\nExample:\n\n```typescript\ndata/\n \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 portfolio.ts\n \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 projects.ts\n \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 blogs.ts\n \342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 skills.ts\n```\n\nUI components must only consume data.\n\nExample:\n\n```typescript\nconst projects = portfolioRepository.getProjects();\n```\n\nNever write:\n\n```tsx\n<h1>Mohamed Irsath Kareem</h1>\n```\n\nInstead:\n\n```tsx\n<h1>{profile.name}</h1>\n```\n\n---\n\n# Theme\n\nUse only one theme.\n\nDark theme only.\n\nDesign inspiration:\n\n* Linear\n* Vercel\n* Raycast\n* Stripe\n* Framer\n\nColor palette:\n\n```css\nBackground: #050816\nSurface: #0f172a\nPrimary: #38bdf8\nSecondary: #8b5cf6\nText: #f8fafc\nMuted: #94a3b8\n```\n\n---\n\n# Responsive Requirements\n\nMust support:\n\n* Mobile\n* Tablet\n* Desktop\n* Ultra Wide Monitors\n\nBreakpoints:\n\n```text\nsm\nmd\nlg\nxl\n2xl\n```\n\nEvery section must be responsive.\n\n---\n\n# Routing Structure\n\nUse React Router.\n\nRoutes:\n\n```text\n/\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 Home\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 About\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 Projects\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 Blogs\n\342\224\234\342\224\200\342\224\200 Skills\n\342\224\224\342\224\200\342\224\200 Contact\n```\n\nOptional:\n\n```text\n/project/:slug\n/blog/:slug\n```\n\n---\n\n# Navbar\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Glassmorphism\n* Sticky\n* Blur effect\n* Animated active route indicator\n* Smooth route transitions\n\nDesktop:\n\n```text\nLogo\nHome\nAbout\nProjects\nBlogs\nSkills\nContact\n```\n\nMobile:\n\n```text\nHamburger Menu\nAnimated Drawer\n```\n\n---\n\n# Hero Section\n\nFull viewport section.\n\nDisplay:\n\n```text\nMohamed Irsath Kareem\n\nFull Stack Web /\nMobile App Developer\n```\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Typing animation\n* Gradient text\n* Floating particles\n* p5.js animated background\n* Mouse interaction effects\n* Scroll indicator\n\nCTA buttons:\n\n```text\nView Projects\nRead Blogs\nContact Me\n```\n\nAnimations:\n\n* Fade\n* Scale\n* Parallax\n* Stagger\n\n---\n\n# About Section\n\nProfessional introduction.\n\nHighlight:\n\n* Full Stack Development\n* Mobile Development\n* Cloud Native Engineering\n* DevOps\n\nTimeline layout.\n\nAnimated cards.\n\nStatistics:\n\n```text\nYears Experience\nProjects Built\nArticles Written\nTechnologies Used\n```\n\nCounter animations.\n\n---\n\n# Skills Section\n\nCreate categorized skill groups.\n\n## Frontend\n\n* ReactJS\n* TypeScript\n* JavaScript\n* Vite\n* NextJS\n* TanStack Query\n\n## Backend\n\n* Spring Boot\n* Java\n* Kotlin\n* Spring Cloud\n* SQL\n* NoSQL\n* Testing\n\n## DevOps\n\n* Docker\n* Kubernetes\n* Helm\n* Terraform\n* ArgoCD\n* AWS\n* GCP\n* Jenkins\n* GitHub Actions\n\n## Mobile\n\n* Jetpack Compose\n* Compose Multiplatform\n* Kotlin Multiplatform\n* Koin\n* Room\n* Ktor\n* Coil\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Animated skill cards\n* Hover effects\n* Progress indicators\n* Scroll reveal\n\n---\n\n# Projects Section\n\n## Mini Projects\n\nDisplay:\n\n```text\nJetpack Compose Animations\nCustom Layout Experiments\nCompose Multiplatform UI Showcases\nAnimation Labs\n```\n\nUse horizontal animated cards.\n\n---\n\n## Major Projects\n\n### Codehorn\n\nShow:\n\n```text\nTitle\nDescription\nTechnologies\nScreenshots\nGithub\nDemo\n```\n\n---\n\n### NoteMyShow\n\nShow:\n\n```text\nTitle\nDescription\nTechnologies\nScreenshots\nGithub\nDemo\n```\n\n---\n\n### Mobile Applications\n\nDisplay as project collection.\n\nUse masonry layout.\n\nAnimations:\n\n* Hover lift\n* Glow effect\n* Tilt effect\n* Stagger reveal\n\n---\n\n# Blogs Section\n\nSources:\n\n## Medium Articles\n\nDisplay:\n\n```text\nFeatured Articles\nLatest Articles\nPopular Articles\n```\n\n---\n\n## Internal Articles\n\nSupport:\n\n```text\nMarkdown Rendering\nSyntax Highlighting\nTable of Contents\nReading Time\n```\n\nBlog Cards:\n\n```text\nThumbnail\nTitle\nTags\nDate\nRead Time\n```\n\nAnimations:\n\n```text\nSlide Up\nFade In\nScale\n```\n\n---\n\n# Contact Section\n\nModern card layout.\n\nFields:\n\n```text\nName\nEmail\nSubject\nMessage\n```\n\nFeatures:\n\n* Validation\n* Animated inputs\n* Success animation\n\nAdditional links:\n\n```text\nGithub\nLinkedIn\nMedium\nEmail\n```\n\n---\n\n# Footer\n\nInclude:\n\n```text\nName\nTagline\nNavigation Links\nSocial Links\nCopyright\n```\n\nAnimated divider.\n\n---\n\n# Animation Requirements\n\nUse Framer Motion extensively.\n\nRequirements:\n\n### Scroll Animations\n\n```text\nFade Up\nFade Left\nFade Right\nScale\nRotate\n```\n\n### Hover Animations\n\n```text\nLift\nGlow\nMagnetic Button\nTilt Card\n```\n\n### Page Transitions\n\n```text\nRoute Transition\nShared Layout Animation\n```\n\n### Advanced\n\nUse Intersection Observer.\n\nTrigger animations only when visible.\n\n---\n\n# p5.js Requirements\n\nCreate an interactive background system.\n\nPossible effects:\n\n```text\nParticle Network\nConstellation\nFloating Dots\nInteractive Mouse Trails\n3D Wireframe Sphere\nNeural Network Visualization\n```\n\nPerformance optimized.\n\nDisable heavy effects on mobile.\n\n---\n\n# Performance Requirements\n\nImplement:\n\n```text\nLazy Loading\nCode Splitting\nMemoization\nImage Optimization\nRoute-based Chunking\n```\n\nUse:\n\n```typescript\nReact.lazy()\nSuspense\n```\n\n---\n\n# Accessibility\n\nImplement:\n\n```text\nARIA Labels\nKeyboard Navigation\nFocus States\nSemantic HTML\n```\n\n---\n\n# SEO\n\nAdd:\n\n```text\nMeta Tags\nOpenGraph Tags\nTwitter Tags\nStructured Data\nSitemap\nRobots.txt\n```\n\n---\n\n# Deliverables\n\nGenerate:\n\n1. Complete React + TypeScript project\n2. Tailwind configuration\n3. React Router setup\n4. Reusable component architecture\n5. Data layer implementation\n6. Responsive layouts\n7. Framer Motion animations\n8. p5.js interactive background\n9. Blog system architecture\n10. Production-ready codebase\n\nThe final result should feel like a premium developer portfolio comparable to Linear, Vercel, Framer, and modern SaaS landing pages, with smooth animations, strong visual hierarchy, dark aesthetic, and excellent performance.\n"
    }
  }
}
