    modified_response: "I will create the `/src/pages/Home.tsx` page representing our primary viewport. This includes the prominent title \"Mohamed Irsath Kareem\", a real-time reactive developer typing animation executing across full-stack titles, an integrated statistics board displaying reactive counter matrices, and highly-styled bento CTAs leading visitors deep into the projects or blogs."
