pointer\\\"><span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold\\\">LinkedIn</span><svg class=\\\"w-4 h-4 text-[#94a3b8] group-hover:text-white\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\\\"/></svg></div><div class=\\\"col-span-7 row-span-2 flex items-end justify-between px-2 pb-2\\\"><div class=\\\"flex gap-12\\\"><div class=\\\"flex flex-col gap-1\\\"><span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#94a3b8] uppercase font-bold tracking-tighter\\\">Based In</span><span class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">Colombo, LK</span></div><div class=\\\"flex flex-col gap-1\\\"><span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#94a3b8] uppercase font-bold tracking-tighter\\\">Specialization</span><span class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">Cloud Native App Eng</span></div><div class=\\\"flex flex-col gap-1\\\"><span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#94a3b8] uppercase font-bold tracking-tighter\\\">Status</span><span class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">Open for Freelance</span></div></div><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4 text-[#94a3b8] text-[10px] font-mono\\\"><span>EST. 2024</span><span class=\\\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-white/20\\\"></span><span>V.1.0.2</span></div></div></main></div>\\n  </body>\\n</html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Immersive UI\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Immersive UI\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML: <!doctype html>\\n<html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n  <head>\\n    <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n    <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n    <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n    <style>\\n      body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n      /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n      .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n      .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n      .flex { display: flex; }\\n      .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n      .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n    </style>\\n  </head>\\n  <body>\\n    <!DOCTYPE html><div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#050816] text-[#f8fafc] font-sans relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col\\\"><style>@import url(\'https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700;800&display=swap\');body{margin:0;padding:0;font-family:\'Inter\',sans-serif;background-color:#050816}.glass{background:rgba(15,23,42,0.6);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)}.text-gradient{background:linear-gradient(to right,#38bdf8,#8b5cf6);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-clip:text;color:transparent}.glow-blue{box-shadow:0 0 50px -10px rgba(56,189,248,0.3)}.glow-purple{box-shadow:0 0 50px -10px rgba(139,92,246,0.3)}.dot-pattern{background-image:radial-gradient(rgba(148,163,184,0.1) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:24px 24px}</style><div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute -top-20 -left-20 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-[#38bdf8] opacity-10 blur-[120px] rounded-full\\\"></div><div class=\\\"absolute -bottom-20 -right-20 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-[#8b5cf6] opacity-10 blur-[120px] rounded-full\\\"></div><div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 dot-pattern\\\"></div></div><nav class=\\\"h-16 flex items-center justify-between px-8 glass sticky top-0 z-50 shrink-0\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\"><div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 rounded bg-gradient-to-br from-[#38bdf8] to-[#8b5cf6] flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white text-xs\\\">MIK</div><span class=\\\"font-semibold tracking-tight\\\">Irsath Kareem</span></div><div class=\\\"flex gap-8 text-sm font-medium text-[#94a3b8]\\\"><a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"text-white\\\">Home</a><a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-white\\\">About</a><a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-white\\\">Projects</a><a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-white\\\">Blogs</a><a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-white\\\">Skills</a></div><button class=\\\"px-5 py-2 rounded-full bg-white text-[#050816] text-xs font-bold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity\\\">Hire Me</button></nav><main class=\\\"flex-1 p-8 grid grid-cols-12 grid-rows-6 gap-4 relative z-10\\\"><section class=\\\"col-span-7 row-span-4 flex flex-col justify-center pr-12\\\"><div class=\\\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-[#38bdf8] text-xs font-medium mb-6 w-fit\\\"><span class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#38bdf8] animate-pulse\\\"></span>Available for new projects</div><h1 class=\\\"text-6xl font-extrabold leading-[1.1] mb-6\\\">Mohamed Irsath<br/><span class=\\\"text-gradient\\\">Kareem</span></h1><p class=\\\"text-lg text-[#94a3b8] mb-8 leading-relaxed max-w-lg\\\">Full Stack Web & Mobile App Developer specializing in building scalable cloud-native architectures and high-performance cross-platform applications.</p><div class=\\\"flex gap-4\\\"><button class=\\\"px-8 py-4 rounded-xl bg-[#38bdf8] text-[#050816] font-bold text-sm glow-blue\\\">View Projects</button><button class=\\\"px-8 py-4 rounded-xl glass font-bold text-sm border-white/20\\\">Read Articles</button></div></section><div class=\\\"col-span-5 row-span-3 glass rounded-3xl p-6 overflow-hidden flex flex-col\\\"><div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-center mb-4\\\"><h3 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[#94a3b8]\\\">Featured Project</h3><span class=\\\"text-[10px] bg-[#38bdf8]/20 text-[#38bdf8] px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase font-bold\\\">Web + Mobile</span></div><div class=\\\"relative flex-1 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-4 bg-[#050816] border border-white/5\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0f172a] to-transparent z-10\\\"></div><div class=\\\"p-6 relative z-20 flex flex-col h-full justify-end\\\"><h4 class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold mb-2\\\">Codehorn</h4><p class=\\\"text-sm text-[#94a3b8] mb-4 line-clamp-2\\\">A specialized learning platform for developers featuring interactive tutorials and real-time coding labs.</p><div class=\\\"flex gap-2\\\"><span class=\\\"text-[10px] px-2 py-1 glass rounded-md\\\">React</span><span class=\\\"text-[10px] px-2 py-1 glass rounded-md\\\">Kotlin</span><span class=\\\"text-[10px] px-2 py-1 glass rounded-md\\\">AWS</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\\\"col-span-3 row-span-3 glass rounded-3xl p-6 flex flex-col justify-between\\\"><h3 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[#94a3b8]\\\">Core Skills</h3><div class=\\\"space-y-4\\\"><div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\"><div class=\\\"flex justify-between text-xs\\\"><span class=\\\"text-white\\\">Frontend</span><span class=\\\"text-[#38bdf8]\\\">95%</span></div><div class=\\\"h-1 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden\\\"><div class=\\\"h-full bg-[#38bdf8] w-[95%]\\\"></div></div></div><div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\"><div class=\\\"flex justify-between text-xs\\\"><span class=\\\"text-white\\\">Backend</span><span class=\\\"text-[#8b5cf6]\\\">90%</span></div><div class=\\\"h-1 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden\\\"><div class=\\\"h-full bg-[#8b5cf6] w-[90%]\\\"></div></div></div><div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\"><div class=\\\"flex justify-between text-xs\\\"><span class=\\\"text-white\\\">Mobile</span><span class=\\\"text-[#38bdf8]\\\">85%</span></div><div class=\\\"h-1 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden\\\"><div class=\\\"h-full bg-[#38bdf8] w-[85%]\\\"></div></div></div><div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\"><div class=\\\"flex justify-between text-xs\\\"><span class=\\\"text-white\\\">DevOps</span><span class=\\\"text-[#8b5cf6]\\\">80%</span></div><div class=\\\"h-1 bg-white/5 rounded-full overflow-hidden\\\"><div class=\\\"h-full bg-[#8b5cf6] w-[80%]\\\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\\\"col-span-2 row-span-2 glass rounded-3xl p-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center\\\"><div class=\\\"text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-1\\\">15+</div><div class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-[#94a3b8] tracking-widest\\\">Projects Built</div></div><div class=\\\"col-span-2 row-span-1 glass rounded-3xl px-6 flex items-center justify-between group cursor-pointer\\\"><span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold\\\">GitHub</span><svg class=\\\"w-4 h-4 text-[#94a3b8] group-hover:text-white\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\\\"/></svg></div><div class=\\\"col-span-2 row-span-1 glass rounded-3xl px-6 flex items-center justify-between group cursor-pointer\\\"><span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold\\\">LinkedIn</span><svg class=\\\"w-4 h-4 text-[#94a3b8] group-hover:text-white\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14\\\"/></svg></div><div class=\\\"col-span-7 row-span-2 flex items-end justify-between px-2 pb-2\\\"><div class=\\\"flex gap-12\\\"><div class=\\\"flex flex-col gap-1\\\"><span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#94a3b8] uppercase font-bold tracking-tighter\\\">Based In</span><span class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">Colombo, LK</span></div><div class=\\\"flex flex-col gap-1\\\"><span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#94a3b8] uppercase font-bold tracking-tighter\\\">Specialization</span><span class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">Cloud Native App Eng</span></div><div class=\\\"flex flex-col gap-1\\\"><span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#94a3b8] uppercase font-bold tracking-tighter\\\">Status</span><span class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">Open for Freelance</span></div></div><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4 text-[#94a3b8] text-[10px] font-mono\\\"><span>EST. 2024</span><span class=\\\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-white/20\\\"></span><span>V.1.0.2</span></div></div></main></div>\\n  </body>\\n</html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
