    thinking: "**Considering Immersive UI Application**\n\nI\'m now focusing on how to integrate the \"Immersive UI\" design theme. I\'m taking the standard design elements\342\200\224colors, fonts, and so on\342\200\224and thinking how to make them feel immersive. I\'m currently pondering the specific impact on the app, given its current state. I am now considering how the design code fits this new objective, too.\n\n\n**Analyzing Design Code Integration**\n\nI\'ve been looking over the existing CSS to see how to incorporate immersive UI elements. The current color scheme is a good base; I\'m evaluating how to add ambient glows and dot patterns for the background, plus glass-like elements for a more immersive feel. I\'m especially focused on the text gradient and glow effects. Finally, I\'m working with the Tailwind configuration.\n\n\n"
