hunk setups.\',\n    concepts: [\'State Management\', \'Vite Bundler\', \'Framer Motion\', \'Tailwind Grid Systems\'],\n  },\n  {\n    name: \'Spring Boot\',\n    icon: Server,\n    tag: \'MICROSERVICE LAYERS\',\n    level: 90,\n    longDesc: \'Engineering reliable RESTful layers and modular JPA services with secure access integrations, high concurrency setups, and optimized docker builds.\',\n    concepts: [\'Spring MVC\', \'Hibernate ORM\', \'OAuth2 Security\', \'EKS Container Deploy\'],\n  },\n  {\n    name: \'Kotlin\',\n    icon: Zap,\n    tag: \'MODERN CORE LANGUAGE\',\n    level: 98,\n    longDesc: \'Expert level functional and object-oriented programming with advanced generic architectures, asynchronous flow paradigms, and safety compiler checks.\',\n    concepts: [\'Coroutines Flow\', \'Kotlin DSL\', \'High-Order Functions\', \'Multiplatform build.gradle\'],\n  },\n  {\n    name: \'Java\',\n    icon: Coffee,\n    tag: \'ENTERPRISE LEGACY/CORE\',\n    level: 92,\n    longDesc: \'Constructing enterprise-grade virtualization code, managing garbage collector pipelines, concurrent lock structures, and extensive Spring architectures.\',\n    concepts: [\'Virtual Threads\', \'Streams API\', \'Dynamic Proxies\', \'Concurrent Lock API\'],\n  }\n];\n\nexport const Home = () => {\n  const profile = portfolioRepository.getProfile();\n  const majorProjects = portfolioRepository.getProjects(\'major\').slice(0, 2);\n  const [selectedSkillIndex, setSelectedSkillIndex] = useState(0);"
